dct_title_s: Thaïlande, Laos, Viêt Nam, Birmanie, Cambodge = Thailand, Laos, Vietnam, Myanmar, Cambodia / cartographie MairDumont ; imprimé et diffusée en France par l'Institut national de l'information géographique et forestière.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Depth shown by soundings. Legend in German, English, French, and Dutch. Map shows: 4 classes of roads, railways, car ferries, airports, international boundaries, state and national capitals, nature parks, places of interest (culture, nature), scenic routes, archaeological excavations, ruins, wells, and volcanos. Includes photographs of tourist attractions.
dct_publisher_sm: Saint-Mandé : Institut national de l'information géographique et forestière, 2017.
